raw_model: All model data. This table is not curated or cleaned, but is the location of complete data from the Hugging Face API. Use with caution
usage: Model usage indicators, including downloads and likes, as well as timestamp indicating when usage indicators were pulled.
core_model: Core fields representing basic model information.
datasets: Information about datasets used in the model.
metrics: Information about metrics used to evaluate the model.
model_card: Core information found in the model card.
parameters: Model parameter counts and tensor types.
tasks: Tasks the model is designed to be used for.
